            text</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <conbody>
    <section>
      <p>The <xmlatt>dir</xmlatt> attribute identifies or overrides the
        text directionality. The following values are valid:</p>
      <dl
        conref="../../langRef/attributes/universalAttributes.dita#univ-atts/dirvalues">
